#Amara T.

#### Read about Amara and investigate the audit logs. Can you find any evidence of fraud?

**[Click here](https://docs.google.com/document/d/1Wsw61alnuJW1EPdb93Z1s5qo5wNE4xWS-A6mqi4m2fU/edit?usp=sharing) if you would prefer to view the audit logs in a document.**

---
## USER PROFILE

* **Age**: 17
* **Location**: El Paso, Texas
* **Background**: Mexican-American, bilingual (Spanish and English), lives with her dad and younger brother
* **School**: Public high school student; takes dual-enrollment classes at a local community college
* **Devices**: iPhone SE, school-issued Chromebook, Xbox Series S
* **Tech Habits**: Heavy gamer (FIFA, Fortnite); active on Discord, Twitch, and Instagram; often uses public Wi-Fi at the rec center
* **Spending Habits**: Uses prepaid Visa gift cards; buys game credits and skins
* **Hobbies**: Soccer, music production (GarageBand), hangs out at the community rec center
* **Travel History**: Frequently visits family in Juárez, Mexico
* **Security Habits**: Uses fingerprint ID; reuses passwords; sometimes forgets to log out of shared or public devices


